INSERT INTO matches (external_id, home_team_id, away_team_id, match_date, status, league_id, league_name, season, score_home, score_away, created_at, updated_at)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.external_id }},
  {{ $json.home_team_id }},
  {{ $json.away_team_id }},
  '{{ $json.match_date }}',
  '{{ $json.status }}',
  {{ $json.league_id }},
  '{{ $json.league_name }}',
  {{ $json.season }},
  {{ $json.score_home }},
  {{ $json.score_away }},
  NOW(),
  NOW()
)
ON CONFLICT (external_id) DO UPDATE SET
  status = EXCLUDED.status,
  score_home = EXCLUDED.score_home,
  score_away = EXCLUDED.score_away,
  updated_at = NOW()

SELECT m.id, t1.name as home, t2.name as away, m.status, m.score_home, m.score_away 
FROM matches m
JOIN teams t1 ON m.home_team_id = t1.id
JOIN teams t2 ON m.away_team_id = t2.id;

SELECT 
  'match' as type, 
  external_id, 
  id 
FROM matches 
WHERE external_id IN ({{ $json.match_ids }})

UNION ALL

SELECT 
  'team' as type, 
  external_id, 
  id 
FROM teams 
WHERE external_id IN ({{ $json.team_ids }})

INSERT INTO events (match_id, minute, extra_time, team_id, player_id, player_name, assist_id, assist_name, type, detail, comments, created_at)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.match_id }},
  {{ $json.minute }},
  {{ $json.extra_time }},
  {{ $json.team_id }},
  {{ $json.player_id }},
  $${{ $json.player_name }}$$,
  {{ $json.assist_id }},
  $${{ $json.assist_name }}$$,
  $${{ $json.type }}$$,
  $${{ $json.detail }}$$,
  $${{ $json.comments }}$$,
  NOW()
)
ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_event DO NOTHING

INSERT INTO teams (external_id, name, logo_url)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.external_id }},
  '{{ $json.name }}',
  '{{ $json.logo_url }}'
)
ON CONFLICT (external_id) DO UPDATE SET
  name = EXCLUDED.name,
  logo_url = EXCLUDED.logo_url

INSERT INTO seasons (year, start_date, end_date, current)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.year }},
  '{{ $json.start_date }}',
  '{{ $json.end_date }}',
  {{ $json.current }}
)
ON CONFLICT (year) DO UPDATE SET
  start_date = EXCLUDED.start_date,
  end_date = EXCLUDED.end_date,
  current = EXCLUDED.current

INSERT INTO leagues (external_id, name, country, logo_url, type)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.external_id }},
  '{{ $json.name }}',
  '{{ $json.country }}',
  '{{ $json.logo_url }}',
  '{{ $json.type }}'
)
ON CONFLICT (external_id) DO UPDATE SET
  name = EXCLUDED.name,
  logo_url = EXCLUDED.logo_url,
  country = EXCLUDED.country,
  type = EXCLUDED.type
SELECT id FROM seasons WHERE year = 2025
SELECT id FROM leagues WHERE external_id = 78

INSERT INTO league_seasons (league_id, season_id, current_round, total_rounds)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.league_id }},
  {{ $json.season_id }},
  '{{ $json.current_round }}',
  {{ $json.total_rounds }}
)
ON CONFLICT (league_id, season_id) DO UPDATE SET
  current_round = EXCLUDED.current_round,
  total_rounds = EXCLUDED.total_rounds

SELECT ls.id 
FROM league_seasons ls
JOIN leagues l ON l.id = ls.league_id
JOIN seasons s ON s.id = ls.season_id
WHERE l.external_id = 78 AND s.year = 2025

INSERT INTO matches (
  external_id, 
  league_season_id, 
  home_team_id, 
  away_team_id, 
  match_date, 
  round, 
  status, 
  score_home, 
  score_away
)
VALUES (
  {{ $json.external_id }},
  {{ $json.league_season_id }},
  (SELECT id FROM teams WHERE external_id = {{ $json.home_team_external_id }}),
  (SELECT id FROM teams WHERE external_id = {{ $json.away_team_external_id }}),
  '{{ $json.match_date }}',
  '{{ $json.round }}',
  '{{ $json.status }}',
  {{ $json.score_home }},
  {{ $json.score_away }}
)
ON CONFLICT (external_id) DO UPDATE SET
  status = EXCLUDED.status,
  score_home = EXCLUDED.score_home,
  score_away = EXCLUDED.score_away

  extra_time,
  team_id,
  player_id,
  player_name,
  assist_id,
  assist_name,
  type,
  detail,

  (SELECT id FROM matches WHERE external_id = {{ $json.match_external_id }}::integer),
  {{ $json.minute }},
  {{ $json.extra_time }},
  (SELECT id FROM teams WHERE external_id = {{ $json.team_external_id }}::integer),

  {{ $json.assist_id }},
  $${{ $json.assist_name }}$$,

  $${{ $json.detail }}$$,
  $${{ $json.comments }}$$
)
